Physics-Udunits2
================

This modules is a OO-interface to Unidata's udunits-2 C-unit library.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   export UDUNITS2_LIBDIR=/my/home/udunits2/lib
   export UDUNITS2_INCDIR=/my/home/udunits2/include
   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

UDUNITS_LIBDIR and UDUNITS_INCDIR is only required if udunits2 is not installed
in standard places like /usr, /usr/local, /opt, /opt/local

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires the following library:

 udunits-2 package from http://www.unidata.ucar.edu/software/udunits/ 

